        {
            "title": "加拿大經濟年初小幅成長 油價衝擊前保持穩步運行",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"Statistics Canada\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"665\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/FOqZBpsPd_XjWQ2eVtYo7A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY2NQ--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/b92f74c3d0b867d1d6496efbe5f0bb60\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"><span>Statistics Canada</span></figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 加拿大實際國內生產毛額（GDP）年初小幅成長，顯示在伊朗戰爭引發油價衝擊之前，經濟仍在穩步前行。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">加拿大統計局周二公佈，1月，行業法實際GDP成長0.1%，初步數據顯示2月成長0.2%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">1月成長主要由商品生產部門帶動，該部門連續第二個月成長0.2%。采礦、采石以及石油和天然氣開采的成長，抵消了製造業的下滑。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">汽車及零組件製造錄得自2021年9月以來最大降幅，下降10.8%。加拿大統計局指出，冬季汽車工廠季節性停工延續至1月，抑制了汽車生產和出口。汽車產量下降23.5%。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-663797ef-e465-3df1-be2f-d687733f2357-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">汽車生產停滯還導致躉售貿易下降1.2%。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"665\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/ilj3DFKFMFVH6Ycei1CSFw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY2NQ--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/bad422f63ea75a091730afce7d6e9247\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">彭博調查的經濟學家此前預計，1月加拿大經濟將保持平穩，這與加拿大統計局對該月的初步估計一致。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">1月和2月的疲軟成長，延續了2025年末加拿大經濟趨弱態勢，因為關稅持續擠壓企業。根據更完整的支出法數據，加拿大第四季度實際GDP按折年率計算下降0.6%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Canada Economy Grew Modestly Ahead of Iran War Energy Shock (1)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Mario Baker Ramirez.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"bloomberg.com\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%8A%A0%E6%8B%BF%E5%A4%A7%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E5%B9%B4%E5%88%9D%E5%B0%8F%E5%B9%85%E6%88%90%E9%95%B7-%E6%B2%B9%E5%83%B9%E8%A1%9D%E6%93%8A%E5%89%8D%E4%BF%9D%E6%8C%81%E7%A9%A9%E6%AD%A5%E9%81%8B%E8%A1%8C-143829652.html",
