        {
            "title": "邁威爾科技股價因與英偉達合作及20億美元投資而飆升11%",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/a6RCAuwenlClVnuZ1wBDBw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEABU081_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"邁威爾\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:邁威爾;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/邁威爾\">邁威爾</a>科技(NASDAQ:MRVL)股價週二大漲11%,此前該公司宣布與<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"英偉達\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:英偉達;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/英偉達\">英偉達</a>達成戰略合作夥伴關係,並獲得這家晶片製造商20億美元的投資。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此次合作透過英偉達NVLink Fusion將<span><span>邁威爾</span></span>連接至英偉達的AI工廠和AI-RAN生態系統,這是一個機架級平台,使客戶能夠利用英偉達NVLink生態系統開發半客製化AI基礎設施。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據協議,邁威爾將提供客製化XPU和與NVLink Fusion相容的擴展網路,而<span><span><span><span>英偉達</span></span></span></span>將提供支援技術,包括Vera CPU、ConnectX網路介面卡、Bluefield DPU、NVLink互連和Spectrum-X交換機,以及機架級AI運算。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-d3a51eac-ca7c-3cb3-b7a8-e6ec8283c3ce-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此次合作還包括在矽光子技術方面的協作,旨在透過英偉達Aerial AI-RAN將電信網路轉變為支援5G/6G的AI基礎設施。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">英偉達創辦人兼執行長黃仁勳表示:「推理拐點已經到來。代幣生成需求正在激增,全世界都在競相建設AI工廠。我們與邁威爾攜手合作,使客戶能夠利用英偉達的AI基礎設施生態系統並擴展規模,以建立專門的AI運算。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">邁威爾董事長兼執行長Matt Murphy表示,擴大合作夥伴關係反映了高速連接、光學互連和加速基礎設施在擴展AI方面日益增長的重要性。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">NVLink Fusion平台使開發客製化XPU的客戶能夠建立與英偉達系統完全相容的異構AI基礎設施,允許與英偉達GPU、LPU、網路和儲存平台整合。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%82%81%E5%A8%81%E7%88%BE%E7%A7%91%E6%8A%80%E8%82%A1%E5%83%B9%E5%9B%A0%E8%88%87%E8%8B%B1%E5%81%89%E9%81%94%E5%90%88%E4%BD%9C%E5%8F%8A20%E5%84%84%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87%E8%80%8C%E9%A3%86%E5%8D%8711-130744280.html",
