        {
            "title": "花旗下調美光目標價,指記憶體現貨價格疲軟",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/XiB5xVhQQDW0sYGRm3OnTw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEE6414U_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 花旗週二下調了美光科技(Micron Technology)的目標價,理由是主流產品大幅回落後,DRAM市場現貨價格走弱。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">分析師Atif Malik寫道,「自<span><span><span><span>美光</span></span></span></span>發布財報以來,主流DDR5 16GB DRAM產品價格下跌約6%」,促使該行將目標價從510美元下調17%至425美元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">儘管下調目標價,花旗仍維持其盈利預測,認為美光與超大規模雲端運算業者之間正在進行的談判可能有助於穩定合約定價。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-3fef0bf0-62be-3c67-b449-7b5f519181b5-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據Malik表示,記憶體供應商已開始討論「3至5年的戰略或長期協議,以鎖定基本供應量、預付款項,並根據市場狀況調整季度定價」,該分析師表示,即使現貨價格走軟,這應能提供支撐。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">花旗將近期價格下跌與對TurboQuant的擔憂聯繫起來,指出從表面價值來看,效率技術可以降低每次查詢的運算和記憶體成本。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">然而,Malik補充說,此類進步「進一步釋放使用量,最終增加運算/記憶體需求」。花旗預計這一動態將反映DeepSeek的影響,認為更便宜的技術在歷史上「增加了對更多技術的需求」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該報告還概述了KV快取在AI工作負載中的作用,強調其在使模型能夠生成更長、更複雜輸出方面的重要性。花旗指出,隨著每個新標記「關注所有先前的標記」,運算強度會上升,這強化了對記憶體的長期結構性需求。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">儘管近期定價壓力持續存在,花旗仍維持與AI驅動需求加速相關的正面長期觀點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%8A%B1%E6%97%97%E4%B8%8B%E8%AA%BF%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%89%E7%9B%AE%E6%A8%99%E5%83%B9-%E6%8C%87%E8%A8%98%E6%86%B6%E9%AB%94%E7%8F%BE%E8%B2%A8%E5%83%B9%E6%A0%BC%E7%96%B2%E8%BB%9F-130216855.html",
